### ============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION (Public - No Token Required)
### ============================================================================

### Register New User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "test123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "test123"
}

### ============================================================================
### USER PROFILE (Protected - Requires X-API-TOKEN)
### ============================================================================

### Get Current User Profile
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/current
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

### Update User Profile
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/current
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

{
  "name": "Updated Name"
}

### Update User Password
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/current
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

{
  "password": "newpassword123"
}

### Logout User
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/current
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

### ============================================================================
### CONTACTS (Protected - Requires X-API-TOKEN)
### ============================================================================

### Create Contact
POST http://localhost:3000/api/contacts
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

{
  "first_name": "John1",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "email": "john1.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "08123456789"
}

### Get Contact by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

### Update Contact
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1404
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

{
  "first_name": "John John 34",
  "last_name": "Smith",
  "email": "john.smith@example.com",
  "phone": "08987654321"
}

### Search Contacts (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/contacts?name=john&email=example.com&page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

### Delete Contact
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

### ============================================================================
### ADDRESSES (Protected - Requires X-API-TOKEN)
### ============================================================================

### Create Address for Contact
POST http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1404/addresses
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

{
  "street": "Jl. Sudirman No.8",
  "city": "Jakarta",
  "province": "DKI Jakarta",
  "country": "Indonesia",
  "postal_code": "10110"
}

### Get Address by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1/addresses/1
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

### List All Addresses for Contact
GET http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1/addresses
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

### Update Address
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1404/addresses/681
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b

{
  "street": "Jl. Sudirman No. 12",
  "city": "Jakarta Selatan",
  "province": "DKI Jakarta",
  "country": "Indonesia",
  "postal_code": "12190"
}

### Delete Address
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/contacts/1/addresses/1
Accept: application/json
X-API-TOKEN: 44a0ab89-2b97-49fb-8354-27593af5369b
